Hanan Name Meaning in English

What does the name Hanan mean? What is the meaning of the name Hanan, lucky number, lucky stone, origin and religion.

Hanan is a name of Semitic origin. In Hebrew it is a masculine name, of the meaning "gracious", "gracious gift"or "grace". In Arabic it means "compassion". The name John is speculated to derive, via Latin and Greek, from the Hebrew name Yehohanan or Yohanan meaning "Yahweh is gracious".
